Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.92,0:03:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{As in, using the restroom?}Như khi đi vệ sinh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.17,0:03:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{Master!}Sư phụ!
